"{\"uid\": \"people.com-olympic-skateboarder-arisa-trew-parents-promised-pet-duck-won-gold-medal-8692281\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ducks are really cute and I really wanted a pet duck,\\\" Arisa Trew, the youngest Australian to win an Olympic gold medal, told reporters  A. Perez Meca/Europa Press via Getty; Getty  Skateboarder Arisa Trew made history on Tuesday, Aug. 7 at the2024 Paris Olympicsas the youngest Australian to win a medal, and she will have something special waiting for her at home: a pet duck.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 379, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 56, \"end\": 61, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4109647679271892e-14, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}, {\"begin\": 141, \"end\": 146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"score\": 0.9993939315876018, \"rank\": 0.0004936523682005039, \"text\": \"Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CJ_Perez\"}, {\"begin\": 152, \"end\": 164, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europa_Press\", \"score\": 0.99999983288491, \"rank\": 1.6711517467049976e-07, \"text\": \"Europa Press\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europa_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Europa_Press\"}, {\"begin\": 176, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"score\": 0.9996197602427853, \"rank\": 0.0003753409746782279, \"text\": \"Getty\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Getty_Images\"}, {\"begin\": 183, \"end\": 195, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0087449146051356e-33, \"text\": \"Skateboarder\", \"types\": [\"Q349\", \"Q1914636\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Skateboarding\"}, {\"begin\": 196, \"end\": 201, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4109647679271892e-14, \"text\": \"Arisa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Arisa\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During apress conferenceafter her victory, the 14-year-old said her parents promised her she could get a pet duck if she won a gold medal.\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 519, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Ducks are really cute and I really wanted a pet duck,\\\" Trew told reporters when asked about her unconventional gift choice.\", \"from\": 521, \"to\": 645, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ulrik Pedersen/DeFodi Images via Getty  Never miss a story - sign up forPEOPLE's free daily newsletterto stay up-to-date on the best of what PEOPLE has to offer\\u200b\\u200b, from celebrity news to compelling human interest stories.\", \"from\": 647, \"to\": 868, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My parents definitely would not let me get a dog or a cat because we are traveling so much right now,\\\" Trew also told Australia'sNine News.\", \"from\": 870, \"to\": 1010, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 989, \"end\": 998, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9793305854049315, \"rank\": 0.012210722904651243, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I feel like a duck might be a little bit easier, and...\", \"from\": 1011, \"to\": 1071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know, I just want a duck.\\\"\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1107, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trew earned her gold medal in women's park skateboarding on Tuesday after scoring a 93.18 on her final run, reportsThe Associated Press.\", \"from\": 1109, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1228, \"end\": 1244, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999879782991, \"rank\": 1.2021878261242584e-08, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kokana Hiraki of Japan and Sky Brown of Great Britain won silver and bronze, respectively.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1336, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1268, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.880259508963412, \"rank\": 0.07544091054127677, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}, {\"begin\": 1273, \"end\": 1282, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sky Brown\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sky_Brown\"}, {\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9760504401850892, \"rank\": 0.02442556721344239, \"text\": \"Great Britain\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Great_Britain_at_the_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hiraki, 16, became Japan's youngest medal winner during the 2020 Tokyo Olympics when she won bronze in the same event at 13.\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1356, \"end\": 1361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"score\": 0.880259508963412, \"rank\": 0.07544091054127677, \"text\": \"Japan\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Japan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It feels amazing having the gold medal around my neck,\\\" Trew told reporters.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1540, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been my goal since watching the Tokyo 2020 Olympics.\", \"from\": 1541, \"to\": 1599, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That inspired me and made me want to come to this Olympics and get to the podium, which is, like, amazing.\\\"\", \"from\": 1600, \"to\": 1707, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The PEOPLE Puzzler crossword is here!\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1746, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"How quickly can you solve it?\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Play now!\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1786, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Trew was born in Cairns, Queensland, and attendsLVLUP, an academy on Australia's Gold Coast where students can study and practice skateboarding.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1932, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1805, \"end\": 1811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairns\", \"score\": 0.9999694100906167, \"rank\": 2.951188040524205e-05, \"text\": \"Cairns\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairns\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cairns\"}, {\"begin\": 1813, \"end\": 1823, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"score\": 0.5937116531813177, \"rank\": 0.6204586878557862, \"text\": \"Queensland\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Queensland\"}, {\"begin\": 1857, \"end\": 1866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9793305854049315, \"rank\": 0.012210722904651243, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She won two gold medals at the 2023 X Games and two golds at the 2024 X Games.\", \"from\": 1933, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This was Trew's first trip to the Olympics and her parents Simon and Aiko Trew watched and cheered her on from the stands at La Concorde.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They struggled to find the words to describe their feelings after Trew's win.\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2228, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Ulrik Pedersen/DeFodi Images via Getty  \\\"We can not believe it.\", \"from\": 2230, \"to\": 2293, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crazy, crazy, absolutely crazy,\\\" Simon toldNine News.\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yeah, it's just do not know what to say.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's just somebody who loves skateboarding and having fun.\\\"\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Skateboard legend Tony Hawk congratulated Trew, Hiraki, Brown and the other skateboarding Olympians on Tuesday.\", \"from\": 2456, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Congratulations to@arisa_trewon her epic last run in women's park finals this afternoon, landing her to a well-deserved gold medal,\\\"Hawk wroteon Instagram.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2725, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Thanks to all of the competitors for pushing skateboarding into a new era of equality and inclusivity.\", \"from\": 2726, \"to\": 2829, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And congrats to \\ud83e\\udd48@cocona.hiraki& \\ud83e\\udd49@skybrown.\\\"\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2875, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"To learn more about all the Olympic and Paralympic hopefuls, come topeople.comto check out ongoing coverage before, during and after the games.\",